{"tid":308723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"比一罐可樂更輕！LG 新 8 吋平板發表","createTime":"2017-07-04T12:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T12:24:23.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68f71a3428bfe6b65d78de386427f37e24e72747","tid":308723,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"平板電腦近年鮮見突破，廠商要為新產品找出吸引消費者買機的賣點絕不容易。LG 日前發表了全新 Android 平板 G Pad IV 8.0 FHD，規格算不上突出，就連系統版本都並非最新，正當以為新平板是另一中庸之作，LG 賦予了它一個讓消費者容易記住的賣點。<br />\n<br />\n這部 8 吋平板的重量只得 290 克，和一罐 250 毫升的可樂的重量相若，這比起市面上相同尺寸的平板都要輕，這個賣點相信能夠吸引經常帶著平板外出工作的用戶。除此以外，LG G Pad IV 8.0 FHD 的另一賣點就是有 4G LTE，就算沒有 Wi-Fi 亦可以連接上網。<br />\n<br />\nLG G Pad IV 8.0 FHD 配備一枚 8 吋 1,920 x 1,080 解像度螢幕，搭配 Snapdragon 435 處理器、2GB RAM 和 32GB 儲存。前後鏡頭均為 5MP，並且有容量略小的 3,000mAh 電池。這部平板由即日起在韓國電訊商 LG U+ 發售，售價約 HK$2,392。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4467/68431/1/1/132437/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fpad%2Ftalk%2F4467%2F68431%2F1%2F1%2F132437%2F&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UI6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=a3a045fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/pad/talk/4467/68431/1/1/132437/</a>"},{"pid":"dbc43e1e0c3f4f5cf840be9089469fe1eaa86a7c","tid":308723,"uid":12055,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"睇錯左<br />\n以為係比一罐可樂更便宜"},{"pid":"63ecf263c709d06816b98c666850e59bd95fa6de","tid":308723,"uid":281,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39a321ea786783c5b391c38a078995cd480089a7","tid":308723,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔買iPad mini 2<br />\n好撚on9 LG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c91205250cb984e879ca908db947a7eb9dd0ea0","tid":308723,"uid":120859,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意apple，應該話係討厭<br />\n但係買娛樂用tabl